{"tid":197112,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"留名等睇熱血市民話鄭松泰係因為梁游兩人而被捕","createTime":"2017-04-11T16:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T22:25:40.000Z","uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bffbf12447f0338873d361abd6e1acb53e3cbb0a","tid":197112,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:49:35.000Z","msg":"去年十月十九日的立法會會議，原訂安排劉小麗、梁頌恆與游蕙禎宣誓，但建制派杯葛會議離場，在點算法定人數期間，鄭松泰將建制派議員插在桌上的區旗和國旗倒插。<br />\n<br />\n本民青迫害熱血又一力證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe1e57b7ad21830c7ddfe3d336d66fabadf6b39","tid":197112,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:51:58.000Z","msg":"豬隊友幼稚小朋友又拖累我地本土建國大業"},{"pid":"242cb5d38b5413b53e96b1f2b7888a406cb69375","tid":197112,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:55:26.000Z","msg":"連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 建國未來"},{"pid":"7e86940636c4dd3ab985b7f1d48ad38eab58849d","tid":197112,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:06:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79814cec946488fd3f810c6565bb398bfbfbfa15","tid":197112,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:12:58.000Z","msg":"夠啦，唔好玩分化啦"},{"pid":"cdfc48448ae623e3b6186720c5348f7bfb322e0e","tid":197112,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豬隊友幼稚小朋友又拖累我地本土建國大業</blockquote><br />\n無梁游就唔會有建制派流會<br />\n泰博就可以安心喺議會建國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb776dd7244ba41453541a89858cdf6c4214b83","tid":197112,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夠啦，唔好玩